                  艺创全能AI知识库系统
                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  全能AI知识库系统Java版，基于前后端分离架构以及Vue3、uni-app、SpringBoot2.5技术栈开发，包含PC端、H5端。该系统支持问答式和文档式知识库，能够导入txt、doc、docx、pdf、md等多种格式文档。
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm font-medium">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                    </svg>
                    多格式导入
                  </div>
                  <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm font-medium">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
