                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-600 dark:text-green-300 text-sm font-medium">
